OL,3,C'A ticking time bomb' - Man diagnosed
OL,4,Cwith Hep B, Hep C and then HIV
OL,6,FA man who was diagnosed with hepatitis
OL,7,FB, hepatitis C and HIV has spoken to
OL,8,FITV News about how he felt like a
OL,9,F"ticking time bomb".
OL,11,FNeil Walker has been ill for most of
OL,12,Fhis life after he was given products
OL,13,Fwhen he was a baby.
OL,15,FHe was given the infected blood
OL,16,Fproducts as part of treatment for
OL,17,Fhaemophilia, leading to him testing
OL,18,Fpositive for HIV when he was 12 years
OL,19,Fold.
