OL,3,C'A ticking time bomb' - Man diagnosed
OL,4,Cwith Hep B, Hep C and then HIV
OL,6,FNow in his 50s, Neil still remembers
OL,7,Fvividly how his life changed
OL,8,Fovernight. He explained: "They had to
OL,9,Fhave special measures put in place.
OL,11,F"Full-time bodyguards, carers carrying
OL,12,Fbleach around with them, first aid
OL,13,Fkits, escorting me to every lesson,
OL,14,Fsitting in on every lesson in case I
OL,15,Fcut myself and they could clear it up."
OL,17,FHe adds: "I had kids screaming to me
OL,18,Fdown the corridors; 'It's the Aids
OL,19,Fkid, it's the kid with Aids, run.'
