OL,3,C'A ticking time bomb' - Man diagnosed
OL,4,Cwith Hep B, Hep C and then HIV
OL,6,F"I could go out at break time, but who
OL,7,Fwants to hang around with a kid with
OL,8,FAids"
OL,10,FNeil, who is from , is one of 30,000
OL,11,Fpeople in the UK who were given
OL,12,Ftreatments infected with HIV and
OL,13,Fhepatitis C during the 1970s and 80s.
OL,15,FWhen Neil was 14, he was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital with a suspected ruptured
OL,17,Fappendix.
OL,19,FHe said there was no compassion or
OL,20,Fcare and he was made to feel like a
OL,21,Fleper with the door padlocked.
