OL,3,C'A ticking time bomb' - Man diagnosed
OL,4,Cwith Hep B, Hep C and then HIV
OL,6,FHe told ITV News Central: "My mother
OL,7,Fwasn't allowed in the room, it was
OL,8,Fbasically padlocked.
OL,10,F"Bedpans were piling up in the room
OL,11,Fand people were coming in with big
OL,12,Fgowns on.
OL,14,F"Two or three surgeons refused to
OL,15,Foperate on me and a surgeon came from
OL,16,FLondon to do the operation."
OL,18,FThat same year, Neil was told he had
OL,19,FHepatitis B. Seven years later he was
OL,20,Fdiagnosed with hepatitis C, and later,
OL,21,FAids.
