OL,3,C'A ticking time bomb' - Man diagnosed
OL,4,Cwith Hep B, Hep C and then HIV
OL,6,FHe said: "I was scared, a total
OL,7,Femotional wreck.
OL,9,F"I didn't want to be here. I didn't
OL,10,Fwant to be a burden to my family."
OL,12,FHis life started to spiral out of
OL,13,Fcontrol, he said: "I didn't care if I
OL,14,Flived or died. Many times I thought of
OL,15,Fdriving my car into the wall."
OL,17,FNeil said he would never be able to
OL,18,Fforgive those who treated him:
OL,19,F"They've given me a life sentence and
OL,20,Feverybody else, and I've lost a lot of
OL,21,Ffriends."
