OL,6,FHe described his wife Tina as his rock
OL,7,Fand soulmate. He says marrying her was
OL,8,Fthe best thing that ever happened to
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FBut because of his illness, there have
OL,12,Fbeen many challenges for the couple
OL,13,Falong the way.
OL,15,FTina said: "There's been times when
OL,16,Fit's not been easy at all. Especially
OL,17,Fwhen he went on a certain treatment
OL,18,Ffor hepatitis C.
