OL,6,F"It was a person that I did not
OL,7,Frecognise and we were going to get
OL,8,Fdivorced because I couldn't do it
OL,9,Fanymore."
OL,11,FThe final report by the government's
OL,12,Finquiry into the infected blood
OL,13,Fscandal is due to be published today.
OL,15,FNeil wants there to be accountability,
OL,16,Fsaying: "Why don't they just pull
OL,17,Ftheir finger out and pay out the
OL,18,Fcompensation?
